Package: curvish
Type: Package
Title: Uses Bayesian GAMMs to Regions Where Slopes Differ
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("John", "Flournoy", email = "john_flournoy@g.harvard.edu",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Uses Bayesian generalized additive mixed models to estimate 
  curves through data and the uses the posterior derivative to compare points
  along those curves in order to determine regions of difference from steepest
  slope.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
